{
  "bio": [
    "Sachin Agarwal is the chairman of PTC Industries, which makes precision stainless steel castings for the power, aerospace and oil and gas sectors.",
    "The business has its roots in an engineering foundry started by his father Sateesh Agarwal in 1963.",
    "Agarwal has a master's degree in finance from Boston College and an MBA from the University of Tulsa in Oklahoma.",
    "His wife Smita is the company's chief financial officer."
  ],
  "about": [
    "The original name of the company was Precision Tools and Castings.",
    "PTC Industries uses robots and 3D printing in its manufacturing processes."
  ]
}